<h1>About This App</h1>

<p>This app helps students calculate their <strong>DP (Due Performance)</strong> mark based on assessments.</p>

<h3>How to Use:</h3>
<ol>
    <li>Each row in the table represents an assessment (like a test or assignment).</li>
    <li>Edit the <strong>name</strong>, <strong>weight (%)</strong>, and <strong>score</strong> for each assessment.</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Add Assessment</strong> to add a new row.</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Delete</strong> to remove an assessment you don't need.</li>
    <li>Click <strong>Calculate</strong> to get your final DP mark.</li>
</ol>

<p>The result will show your final mark and whether you <span class="text-success fw-bold">Pass</span> or <span class="text-danger fw-bold">Failed</span>.</p>

<hr />

<p><strong>Note:</strong> Make sure the total weight of all assessments adds up to 100% for accurate results.</p>
